| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3426 — Recovery Inhibition (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b09ce8bd-2d9b-5453-8ab7-df5ff4a5968b"
